import pandas as pd

# === 3. Baca CSV dari file yang sudah ada ===
df = pd.read_csv("Sample - Superstore.csv", encoding="latin1")

# ubah nama kolom: spasi â†’ underscore agar aman dipakai
df.columns = df.columns.str.replace(" ", "_")

print("Preview data:")
print(df.head())
print("\nNama kolom:")
print(df.columns)

# === 4. Tipe data ===
print("\nTipe data tiap kolom:")
print(df.dtypes)

# === 5. Kualitas data ===

## 5a. Outlier Analysis (IQR) untuk kolom numerik
def detect_outliers_iqr(data, col):
    Q1 = data[col].quantile(0.25)
    Q3 = data[col].quantile(0.75)
    IQR = Q3 - Q1
    lower = Q1 - 1.5 * IQR
    upper = Q3 + 1.5 * IQR
    outliers = data[(data[col] < lower) | (data[col] > upper)]
    return outliers

print("\nðŸ”Ž Outlier pada kolom Sales:")
outliers_sales = detect_outliers_iqr(df, "Sales")
print(outliers_sales[["Row_ID", "Sales"]].head())

print("\nðŸ”Ž Outlier pada kolom Profit:")
outliers_profit = detect_outliers_iqr(df, "Profit")
print(outliers_profit[["Row_ID", "Profit"]].head())

## 5b. Konsistensi data (contoh: Postal_Code harus numerik)
inconsistent_postal = df[~df["Postal_Code"].astype(str).str.isnumeric()]
print("\nðŸš¨ Data tidak konsisten pada Postal_Code:")
print(inconsistent_postal.head())

## 5c. Missing Values
print("\nðŸ”Ž Jumlah missing values per kolom:")
print(df.isnull().sum())

## 5d. Duplikasi Data
print("\nðŸ”Ž Jumlah data duplikat:", df.duplicated().sum())

# === 6. Ringkasan Statistik ===
print("\nðŸ“Š Ringkasan Statistik Numerik:")
print(df.describe())

# === 2. Buat file .env berisi credential Supabase ===
# Pastikan ini dijalankan di Google Colab. Jika tidak, buat file .env secara manual.
import os

env_content = """
USER=postgres.wzdudprybyachqxjhmpw
PASSWORD=ks9unws6dHe76WJD
HOST=aws-1-us-east-2.pooler.supabase.com
PORT=5432
DBNAME=postgres
"""
with open(".env", "w") as f:
    f.write(env_content)

# === 3. Load env & koneksi ke Supabase PostgreSQL ===
import psycopg2
from dotenv import load_dotenv
import pandas as pd
from google.colab import files

load_dotenv()

USER = os.getenv("USER")
PASSWORD = os.getenv("PASSWORD")
HOST = os.getenv("HOST")
PORT = os.getenv("PORT")
DBNAME = os.getenv("DBNAME")

try:
    conn = psycopg2.connect(
        user=USER,
        password=PASSWORD,
        host=HOST,
        port=PORT,
        dbname=DBNAME
    )
    print("âœ… Connection successful!")
except Exception as e:
    print("âŒ Failed to connect:", e)
    # Keluar dari skrip jika koneksi gagal
    exit()

# === 4. Upload CSV ke Colab ===
# Pastikan file iris-full.csv sudah diunggah ke Colab
print("Silakan unggah file 'iris-full.csv' Anda.")
uploaded = files.upload()

# Baca CSV dengan encoding utf-8 (umum)
try:
    df = pd.read_csv("iris-full.csv", encoding="utf-8")
except UnicodeDecodeError:
    # Coba encoding lain jika gagal
    df = pd.read_csv("iris-full.csv", encoding="latin1")

# Ubah nama kolom agar tidak ada spasi
df.columns = df.columns.str.replace(" ", "_").str.lower()

print("Preview data:")
print(df.head())
print("\nNama kolom yang akan digunakan:")
print(df.columns)
print("\nTipe data per kolom:")
print(df.dtypes)

# === 5. Buat tabel di PostgreSQL jika belum ada ===
cursor = conn.cursor()

create_table_query = """
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS iris (
    id INT,
    class VARCHAR(50),
    sepal_length FLOAT,
    sepal_width FLOAT,
    petal_length FLOAT,
    petal_width FLOAT
);
"""
cursor.execute(create_table_query)
conn.commit()
print("\nâœ… Tabel 'iris' berhasil dibuat atau sudah ada!")

# === 6. Insert data CSV ke PostgreSQL ===
# Hapus semua data di tabel terlebih dahulu untuk menghindari duplikasi
cursor.execute("DELETE FROM iris;")
conn.commit()
print("âœ… Data lama di tabel 'iris' telah dihapus.")

for _, row in df.iterrows():
    cursor.execute("""
        INSERT INTO iris (
            id, class, sepal_length, sepal_width, petal_length, petal_width
        )
        VALUES (%s, %s, %s, %s, %s, %s)
    """, tuple(row))

conn.commit()
print("âœ… Data 'iris' berhasil diunggah ke Supabase!")

# === 7. Cek apakah data berhasil masuk ===
cursor.execute("SELECT COUNT(*) FROM iris;")
print("\nðŸ“Š Total baris dalam tabel 'iris':", cursor.fetchone()[0])

cursor.close()
conn.close()
print("ðŸ”’ Koneksi ditutup.")

# Copy dataset dari Power BI
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split
from sklearn.neighbors import KNeighborsClassifier
from sklearn.metrics import classification_report, confusion_matrix
from sklearn.decomposition import PCA

# Copy dataset dari Power BI
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from sklearn.neighbors import LocalOutlierFactor
from sklearn.decomposition import PCA

# Copy dataset Power BI
dataset = dataset.copy()

# Pilih fitur numerik
X = dataset[['petal length', 'petal width', 'sepal_length', 'sepal_width']]

# KNN Outlier Detection (LOF)
lof = LocalOutlierFactor(n_neighbors=20, contamination=0.05)  # contamination=5% dianggap outlier
y_pred = lof.fit_predict(X)

# Tambah kolom hasil ke dataset
dataset['outlier'] = y_pred  # -1 = outlier, 1 = normal

# PCA untuk visualisasi
pca = PCA(n_components=2)
X_pca = pca.fit_transform(X)

plt.figure(figsize=(6,4))
plt.scatter(
    X_pca[:,0],
    X_pca[:,1],
    c=dataset['outlier'],
    cmap='coolwarm',
    edgecolor='k'
)
plt.xlabel("PCA 1")
plt.ylabel("PCA 2")
plt.title("Outlier Detection dengan KNN (LOF)")
plt.show()

maka output yang keluar seperti ini, script berikut adalah clustering menggunakan K-means -iris masukkan script ini lalu run.

# The following code to create a dataframe and remove duplicated rows is always executed and acts as a preamble for your script:

# dataset = pandas.DataFrame(petal length, petal width, sepal_length, sepal_width)
# dataset = dataset.drop_duplicates()

# Paste or type your script code here:
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from sklearn.cluster import KMeans
from sklearn.decomposition import PCA

# Copy dataset dari Power BI
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from sklearn.cluster import KMeans
from sklearn.decomposition import PCA

# Copy dataset dari Power BI
dataset = dataset.copy()

# Pilih fitur (pakai semua fitur kalau sudah ada di dataset)
X = dataset[['petal length', 'petal width', 'sepal_length', 'sepal_width']]

# K-Means clustering (3 cluster)
kmeans = KMeans(n_clusters=3, random_state=42, n_init=10)
dataset['cluster'] = kmeans.fit_predict(X)

# PCA untuk reduksi dimensi ke 2D
pca = PCA(n_components=2)
X_pca = pca.fit_transform(X)
dataset['pca1'] = X_pca[:, 0]
dataset['pca2'] = X_pca[:, 1]

# Plot
plt.figure(figsize=(6,4))
plt.scatter(
    dataset['pca1'],
    dataset['pca2'],
    c=dataset['cluster'],
    cmap='viridis',
    edgecolor='k'
)
plt.xlabel("PCA 1")
plt.ylabel("PCA 2")
plt.title("Clustering Iris dengan K-Means")
plt.show()
